column5: @CustomerIsFirst If “normal” means working from office 9-5/5 days a week, and spending 20 hrs/wk commuting, I don’t want to go back to normal. The trains to NYC are crowded- pre-pan schd hasn’t returned, and my team is fully remote so when I go in for work, Im still on zoom almost all day.#rto NO
@stephaniethum Sometimes the best golden nuggets come from icky uncomfortable insights. Keep calm and carry on, you’ve got this!
